item.title: CVE-2021-20032|2024-08-03T17:30:06.859Z -- sonicwall -- sonicwall%20analytics%20on-prem
item.description: SonicWall Analytics 2.5 On-Prem is vulnerable to Java Debug Wire Protocol (JDWP) interface security misconfiguration vulnerability which potentially leads to Remote Code Execution. This vulnerability impacts Analytics On-Prem 2.5.2518 and earlier.
